DIRECTIONS: Clearly define a problem or an idea of your choice, where you would need to leverage the Foursquare location data to solve or execute. Remember that data science problems always target an audience and are meant to help a group of stakeholders solve a problem, so make sure that you explicitly describe your audience and why they would care about your problem.

INTRODUCTION/BUSINESS PROBLEM:
Compare types of medical facilities around ten cities in the state of Colorado. Nursing students are about to graduate, and want to relocate to a place with the most potential job opportunities, while staying within the state of Colorado. Finding which types of medical facilities are most prevalent near each city will help them choose which city to move to after graduation, based on their preferred type of future employer.
